{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/Wishlist_Cropped.gif?t=1734076884\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RESIDUAL SOUL is a singleplayer narrative short-story heavily inspired by the creepypasta horror genre.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/Flashlight.gif?t=1734076884\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After being taken to a purgatory-like forest with the promise of speaking to his deceased wife, Matt must survive his time there and bring peace to the souls who still linger. Manage threats like violent souls and fluctuating power levels while unveiling the stories of those who came before you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/extras/Radio.gif?t=1734076884\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Melancholic atmosphere and stunning visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Thoughtful sound design</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Skilled voice acting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 Dynamic storyline<br><br><strong>CONTENT WARNING:</strong><br><i>RESIDUAL SOUL FEATURES MATURE THEMES DEALING WITH LOSS OF LOVED ONES AND SUICIDE. IF SUCH TOPICS MAY EFFECT YOU NEGATIVELY, KINDLY PASS ON THIS GAME.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734076884","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734076884","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3177670/6a3cf2ed56eb1bdbd0c7a81e4c